{"tid":1280344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【致和理非的緊急呼籲 - 組織工會、發動大型罷工】","createTime":"2019-07-03T02:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:00:17.000Z","uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad86348f69556249c0d3bdec3694ee2dd32887d","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"和理非如果真心想贏，真係想避免流血<br />\n唔該你哋 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家 立刻 馬上</span></strong></span> 成立<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正嘅工會</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非最低成本就係發動長期有效嘅罷工<br />\n成立可以真正迫視政府回應訴嘅工會<br />\n如果有二百萬人同時罷工，連中共都唔夠做啲咩<br />\n人數永遠係最佳嘅掩護<br />\n<br />\n如果繼續諗住鳩up咩重奪議會<br />\n絕對係重覆犯錯呀屌你老味<br />\n<br />\n如果連呢個成本和理非都唔願意付出<br />\n所有嘢都只係流於口號<br />\n唔好再up乜柒鬥長命<br />\n香港無咁長命㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n大家同意嘅唔該幫手傳開去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果和理非真心想贏就要行動喇</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c3063248107e8b3bdbc051d555e12613f54eaf08","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a23ba86020e8083fd7c5b1b3afae0dba160bcd2b","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"581e3a1ca0c699ebc37f6b169ee4b46ee1897306","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f8f138d9ee75c4ab5cbcf716f9ab600bac77544f","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33c5709f1b91fac767bdee12d5805135190ef554","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"14c3c9a388fcf1349f60f25e732bfb83d296ec64","tid":1280344,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-0